{"title":"Kona Breaks into Focus w/ Video by Patti V & Colleen Meas For International Women’s Day","link":"https://bikerumor.com/kona-breaks-into-focus-w-video-by-patti-v-colleen-meas-for-international-womens-day/","date":1709949480000,"content":"<p><img width=\"8256\" height=\"5504\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Kona-Bikes-Breaking-into-Focus-golden-hour.jpeg\" alt=\"Kona Bikes Breaking into Focus golden hour\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Kona-Bikes-Breaking-into-Focus-golden-hour.jpeg 8256w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Kona-Bikes-Breaking-into-Focus-golden-hour-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Kona-Bikes-Breaking-into-Focus-golden-hour-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Kona-Bikes-Breaking-into-Focus-golden-hour-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Kona-Bikes-Breaking-into-Focus-golden-hour-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Kona-Bikes-Breaking-into-Focus-golden-hour-1536x1024.jpeg 1536w\" /></p>\n<p><em><strong>From Kona Bikes: </strong>Riding is an inherently solo sport – which means it’s easy to forget that working with others is the key that can unlock the next level of what we’re grinding so hard to accomplish.  </em> </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Patty V and Colleen Meas are two professional creatives who have been banging their fists against the door of the cycling community, wanting desperately to break into the tight-knit media of its industry. </em>  </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Kona-Bikes-Breaking-into-Focus-workin.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Kona-Bikes-Breaking-into-Focus-workin-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"Kona Bikes Breaking into Focus workin'\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Kona-Bikes-Breaking-into-Focus-workin-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Kona-Bikes-Breaking-into-Focus-workin-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Kona-Bikes-Breaking-into-Focus-workin-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Kona-Bikes-Breaking-into-Focus-workin-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Kona-Bikes-Breaking-into-Focus-workin-1536x1024.jpeg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><em>While they have about as much in common as they don’t, their shared obstacles on their journey to being considered for professional cycling media jobs have empowered them to draw attention to the missing piece of the equation. </em> </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Kona-Bikes-Breaking-into-Focus-getting-the-shot.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Kona-Bikes-Breaking-into-Focus-getting-the-shot-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"Kona Bikes Breaking into Focus getting the shot\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Kona-Bikes-Breaking-into-Focus-getting-the-shot-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Kona-Bikes-Breaking-into-Focus-getting-the-shot-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Kona-Bikes-Breaking-into-Focus-getting-the-shot-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Kona-Bikes-Breaking-into-Focus-getting-the-shot-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Kona-Bikes-Breaking-into-Focus-getting-the-shot-1536x1024.jpeg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><em>This International Women’s Day, we’re honored to be able to shine a light on Patty and Colleen’s collaboration journey and bring attention to the women who are out there kicking ass and kicking down doors with their hard work. Asking for help is incredibly hard, but remembering to answer and offer peer mentorship is something that we simply need to make time for– because odds are, it will make all the difference in the world. </em></p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Kona-Bikes-Breaking-into-Focus-getting-it-done.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Kona-Bikes-Breaking-into-Focus-getting-it-done-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"Kona Bikes Breaking into Focus getting it done\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Kona-Bikes-Breaking-into-Focus-getting-it-done-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Kona-Bikes-Breaking-into-Focus-getting-it-done-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Kona-Bikes-Breaking-into-Focus-getting-it-done-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Kona-Bikes-Breaking-into-Focus-getting-it-done-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Kona-Bikes-Breaking-into-Focus-getting-it-done-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Kona-Bikes-Breaking-into-Focus-getting-it-done.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Jump into this endearing story of a sunny Southern Californian meeting a rugged Pacific Northwesterner halfway up the West Coast to improve their skills, of course, ride bikes, and get the job done – together! </em></p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.konaworld.com/\" target=\"_blank\">KonaWorld.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/kona-breaks-into-focus-w-video-by-patti-v-colleen-meas-for-international-womens-day/\">Kona Breaks into Focus w/ Video by Patti V &amp; Colleen Meas For International Women’s Day</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"f86186b62a5697cbd72edd99d18f17b133e41819745be7afc5f97310f60fb5ba","category":"Cycling"}